{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260325/1113452510720299008430827.jpeg/h02eqEhH3mMSS5Xn9jZ8ti8abTOG18daO3JMKjtyTCo\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\"><p>《紐約時報》報道，美國官員和知情人士透露，由於伊朗領導層在是否參加新一輪和平談判的問題上仍存在分歧，萬斯原定於周二啟程前往伊斯蘭堡的行程被推遲數小時。</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T18:06:45.934557+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":75,"images":1,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}